    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Under the Minimal profile review, the seven assessed credibility factors collectively meet the threshold for acceptance at the declared assurance level. The six not-assessed factors are acknowledged as epistemic gaps and are documented for resolution in a subsequent full assessment. The intended use scope — CFD prediction of hemolysis index for a Class III centrifugal VAD at MRL 5 — is described in the bound Requirement (req/cou2-vad-hemolysis-mrl5) and Claim (claim/cou2-cfd-hemolysis-vad) nodes. The decision team accepts the package under the Minimal profile with the understanding that a Complete profile assessment must be completed prior to regulatory submission.",
